radiographic_examinations.findings: Hepatic parenchyma appears within normal limits; contour of the liver is smooth; no focal liver mass; main portal vein is patent; no ascites; no intrahepatic biliary dilation; gallbladder shows cholelithiasis without gallbladder wall thickening; pancreas appears within normal limits without masses; spleen normal echogenicity; limited views of the right kidney show no hydronephrosis; visualized portions of aorta and IVC are within normal limits.
